      <div class="yoga-highlight-left">
        <h2 class="yoga-highlight-title">DRK Yoga</h2>
        <p class="yoga-highlight-description">
          The art of stillness, the power of black.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="yoga-highlight-button">EXPLORE COLLECTION</a>
